titleInfo.title: Fokes v. Equifax Information Services LLC et al
titleInfo.subTitle: (PRETRIAL SCHEDULING) ORDER signed by Chief Judge Morrison C. England, Jr., on 1/3/14. All discovery, with the exception of expert discovery, shall be completed byJuly 7, 2014. Designation of Expert Witnesses is due by September 4, 2014. The last day to hear dispositive motions shall be January 8, 2015. The Final Pretrial Conference is set for 3/5/2015 at 02:00 PM in Courtroom 7 (MCE) before Chief Judge Morrison C. England, Jr.. The parties shall file, not later than February 12, 2015, a Joint Final Pretrial Conference Statement. The parties shall file trial briefs not later than February 19, 2015. Any evidentiary or procedural motions are to be filed by February 12, 2015.Oppositions must be filed by February 19, 2015, and any reply must be filed by February 26, 2015. The Jury Trial is set for 5/4/2015 at 09:00 AM in Courtroom 7 (MCE) before Chief Judge Morrison C. England, Jr.. The parties estimate a trial length of four (4) days. A Settlement Conference is set for 5/8/2014 at 10:00 AM in Courtroom 27 (DAD) before Magistrate Judge Dale A. Drozd. Each party is directed to submit to the chambers of Judge Dale A. Drozd confidential settlement conference statements not later than May 1, 2014. (Kastilahn, A)
